<bibRefCitation id="EFE44B76FFC7FFCBFA83F9CB143BC522" author="Fluke CT" pageId="16" pageNumber="713" pagination="1 - 83" refId="ref33377" refString="Fluke CT. 1951. Syrphid flies related to Volucella scutellata Macquart. American Museum Novitates 1503: 1 - 83." type="journal article" year="1951">Fluke (1951)</bibRefCitation>
